Precipitation Analysis

Raw precipitation data from 1981 to February 2020

Average yearly precipitation from Jan 1 1981 to Dec 31 2019

Precipitation is decreasing by -0.003404 mm/yr and is statistically signficant, pvalue = 0.02

Evaluate strengths of the trends

  • Average annual precipitation: tau = -0.29, pvalue = 0.01
  • Average spring precipitation: tau = -0.22, pvalue = 0.05
  • Average summer precipitation: tau = -0.13, pvalue = 0.27
  • Average fall precipitation: tau = -0.18, pvalue = 0.11
  • Average winter precipitation: tau = 0.04, pvalue = 0.72
